

FITS package

Covers FITS v3 Standard approx up to Section 4 Header

Supports:
- positioning in FITS file by HDU number
-- over primary HDU and conforming extensions
-- mandatory keys BITPIX NAXIS, NAXISn, and PCOUNT, GCOUNT recognized
- Read/Write IMAGE's to Primary-HDU and Extension-HDU:
-- Read/Write Headers by Cards
-- Read/Write Data as 1 dimensional array (client must convert between N-dim -> 1-dim)

- Endianness not supported
- TABLES not supported
- WCS not supported
- Random Groups and non standard extesions not supported
